In Epi's 3-Ingredient Recipes series, we show you how to make great food with just three ingredients (plus staples like oil, salt, and pepper). A quick toss in sweet, not-too-spicy Korean red pepper sauce makes these wings irresistible, while sliced scallion adds a fresh finish. 

