Savings on 3 ingredient(s) 
Enter Zip to change location: 
Ingredients 
1 can (19 oz) Old El Paso™ red enchilada sauce Save $ 
1 package (1 oz) Old El Paso™ original taco seasoning mix Save $ 
2 tablespoons chili powder 
2 teaspoons dried oregano leaves 
2 teaspoons ground cumin 
2 teaspoons salt 
1 boneless pork shoulder (3 to 4 lb) 
1 carton (32 oz) Progresso™ chicken broth Save $ 
1 can (28 oz) Muir Glen™ organic fire-roasted crushed tomatoes, undrained 
1 can (15.25 oz) whole kernel corn, drained 
