Total 4 hr 10 min 
Servings 6 

Bring the flavors of fall to your table with a pork chop dinner featuring colorful cranberries and comforting stuffing. 
Ingredients 
6 boneless pork loin chops, about 1 inch thick (about 2 1/4 lb) 
