Savory Cheese Cookies 
Christmas Scandinavian Gouda Appetizer +11 
Easy  Parmesan  Gin  Baking Powder  Milk Butter  Snack  Kosher Salt  Flour  Cocktail Party Black Pepper 
Save (10) Rate 
24 cookies Easy  
 (0) Total: 30 min Active: 15 min 
PREVIOUS: 
Checkerboard Cookies 
NEXT: 
Red Velvet Crackle Cookies 
INGREDIENTS (8) 
1 cup room temperature butter 
1/2 cup finely grated aged cheese, such as Gouda or Parmesan 
1 teaspoon kosher salt 
1 teaspoon ground black pepper 
1/2 cup whole milk 
2 tablespoons gin 
2 cups all-purpose flour 
2 teaspoons baking powder 
al Information 
Calories 
