Twice-Cooked Sweet Potatoes with Rosemary, Hazelnuts, and Crème Fraîche 
American Rosemary Hazelnut +16 
Sweet Potato  Side Dish  Crème Fraîche  Fall Easy  Dinner Party  Soy Sauce  Eggs  Olive Oil Oranges  Nutmeg  Molasses  Dinner  Salt Winter  Black Pepper 
Save (1) Rate 
4 servings Easy  
 (0) Total: 1 hr 30 min Active: 20 min 
