Grilled Bok Choy Wedge with Blue Cheese-Buttermilk Dressing 
How to Make Grilled Bok Choy Wedge with Blue Cheese-Buttermilk Dressing 
Grilled bok choy has a pleasantly bitter edge, which is softened by the sweet tomatoes and cooling contrast of tangy blue cheese dressing.  Ready in just 15 minutes, this simple salad is full of fresh ingredients and bold flavors. 
Pause 
Mute 
Current Time 0:00 
