Fat9 g (13.9%) 
Saturated5.3 g (26.3%) 
Trans0.3 g 
Carbs45.2 g (15.1%) 
Fiber6.3 g (25.2%) 
Sugars3.9 g 
Protein8.3 g (16.6%) 
