READY IN: 5mins 
YIELD: 3 cups	UNITS: US 
INGREDIENTS  
2 -3 tablespoons cornstarch 
1⁄4 cup brown sugar, packed 
1⁄4 teaspoon ground ginger (or a bit of fresh minced ginger) 
