1⁄4 cup cider vinegar or 1⁄4 cup white vinegar 
1⁄2 cup water 
1 1⁄2 cups vegetable broth or 1 1⁄2 cups beef broth or 1 1⁄2 cups chicken broth (I use chicken broth if my stir fry will have chicken, etc.) 
DIRECTIONS 
