1 tablespoon chopped onion 
Pinch crushed red pepper flakes 
1 (3-pound) whole chicken, butterflied 
Salt and freshly ground black pepper 
ADD CHECKED ITEMS TO GROCERY LIST 
Directions 
 how to make this recipe. 

