Grilled Chicken Cordon Bleu  
Grilled Chicken Cordon Bleu (03:15) 
Total:20 minPrep: 10 minCook: 10 min 
Yield: 4 servings 
Level: Easy 
 Info  
HEALTHY 
Ingredients 
4 boneless, skinless chicken breasts, pounded thin 
Olive oil 
Salt and freshly ground black pepper 
