Olive oil 
Salt and freshly ground pepper 
8 small new potatoes, cut in half 
Twelve 6-inch flour tortillas 
1 cup Monterey Jack cheese, finely grated 
1 cup white Cheddar cheese, finely grated 
1 head roasted garlic 
