SWEET APPLE SNACK WITH CHOCOLATE 
 your own photos 
What you need:  
1 large or medium gala apple (these are best, but use any kind) 
1 cup of chocolate chips (obviously vegan kind) 
1 cup of roasted peanuts or whatever kind of nut prefered. 

What you do:  
Melt the chocolate chips for about 40 sec. Dont heat till the chips are all melted, because then it would burn. Stir till smooth. 
Place the washe'd but uncut apple on a plate. Pour the chocolate on the apple, then sprinkle the peanuts on top. 
Pop into the freezer for about 5-7 minutes, or howe'ver long it takes to firm up the chocolate. Make sure to not freeze the food though. 
In about 15 min. you have a delicious vegan snack! Enjoy! 

