Kale Frittata 

Kale sprouts with Parmesan and garlic (Steamy Kitchen) 

Balsamic roasted kale sprouts (From a Chef’s Kitchen) 

Spicy sautéed kale sprouts (Body Mind Freedom) 

Kale sprouts (Trader Joe’s) 

